    "This approach reduces the computational burden of ISAC devices and significantly improves computational efficiency, facilitating the implementation of AI-enabled ISAC.",
    "Huang et al. [241] studied the EC-oriented ISAC network, where multiple ISAC devices cooperatively sensed multiple targets in sequence and offloaded their sensing data to the edge server for analysis and processing.",
    "They minimized the total power through joint sensing beamforming, offload beamforming, and sensing schedule design, and developed an effective algorithm to obtain the optimal solution.",
    "Huang et al. [242] investigated the EC-assisted airborne ISAC systems, where a UAV acted as the ISAC-BS to sense multiple targets in sequence and offloaded the sensing data to an edge server for training an AI model.",
    "The system-level cost was minimized subject to model training error and sensing performance constraints."
